# Cross-Chunk Synthesizer — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

**Layer 9 — Cross-Chunk Synthesizer** per §2.9. Takes worker outputs, deduplicates claims, detects contradictions, builds a structured evidence graph, and computes global coverage.

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    WO["Worker Outputs"] --> FILT["Filter SUFFICIENT"]
    FILT --> DEDUP["Claim Dedup<br/>Jaccard > 0.92"]
    DEDUP --> COMP["Complementary Merge<br/>Group by fact components"]
    COMP --> CONF["Conflict Detection<br/>Negation / Antonyms"]
    CONF --> GRAPH["Evidence Graph<br/>Nodes + Edges"]
    GRAPH --> COV["Global Coverage<br/>fact_components ratio"]
    COV --> RESULT["SynthesisResult"]
```

